snippet.title: Kingmakers - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2109770/Kingmakers/

Prepare to rewrite history with Kingmakers, an action/strategy sandbox where you bring guns to a sword fight amidst massive war-torn medieval battles. Build, lead, fight, and change the course of history — coming to PC on Steam, solo, or co-op from the Redemption Road Games team.

Discord: https://discord.gg/kingmakers
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Ian_Fisch
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/kingmakersgame
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@kingmakers_game
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kingmakers_game
Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/@Kingmakers_Game
